                    "type":"link",
                    "target": "_blank",
                    "url":"https://www.jungfrau.ch/en-gb/summer-sport/hiking/",
                    "value":"many other trails"
                },
                {
                    "type":"text",
                    "value":" in the area. When it comes to hiking in the Jungfrau region, you're spoilt for choice. Nature enthusiasts will encounter meticulously marked paths in every direction: leading to summits or serene mountain lakes, winding through valleys or tracing the course of streams. Whether seeking leisurely strolls or aiming for challenging ascents, following the guidance of the yellow arrows ensures you'll navigate your way with ease."
                }
