        {
            "type": "richtext",
            "title": "Activities for Children",
            "titlelevel": 3,
            "text": [
                {
                    "type":"text",
                    "value": "Wengen isn't just a paradise for hiking enthusiasts; it's also a haven for families with children, offering an array of engaging activities to keep the little ones entertained. From thrilling outdoor adventures to captivating indoor experiences, there's something for every child to enjoy. Next, we'll showcase some of the exciting activities tailored for kids, ensuring that families can create unforgettable memories together in this enchanting alpine destination."
                }
            ]
        },


        {
            "type": "richtext",
            "text": [
                {
                    "type": "link",
                    "class": "font-bold uppercase tracking-wide",
                    "target": "_blank",
                    "url":"https://wengen.swiss/en/map/detail/figeler-wengen-c3268848-e134-4396-a122-e957e8e105d5.html",
                    "value": "Figeler Wengen: "
                },
                {
                    "type":"text",
                    "value": "At the Snowgarden, with the lovable mascot \"Snowli\", children are introduced to skiing in a safe and enjoyable environment. With several carpet conveyor belts and an abundance of playful aids, youngsters can navigate the snow with ease and excitement during their initial days on the slopes."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "richtext",
            "text": [
                {
                    "type": "link",
                    "class": "font-bold uppercase tracking-wide",
                    "target": "_blank",
                    "url":"https://wengen.swiss/en/map/detail/wendy-s-winter-mystery-trail-242d0446-11e4-45a6-9c6c-0570de6d9608.html",
                    "value": "Wendy's Winter Mystery Trail: "
                },
                {
                    "type":"text",
                    "value": "To participate, all you require is a smartphone with internet connectivity. You'll be directed to different locations using a virtual map. Once you reach the designated coordinates, the digital content will be displayed on your mobile phone screen."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "richtext",
            "text": [
                {
                    "type": "link",
                    "class": "font-bold uppercase tracking-wide",
                    "target": "_blank",
                    "url":"https://wengen.swiss/en/map/detail/playhouse-day-nursery-d582cedd-a2f4-4a1e-9342-07e0c28131e6.html",
                    "value": "Playhouse day nursery: "
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "Located conveniently next to the Tourist Centre, the Playhouse nursery buzzes with activity, providing a vibrant environment for children. As parents indulge in winter sports amidst the stunning Jungfrau Region, we ensure the well-being of their little ones. Engaging in playful activities, such as games, coloring, crafts, and snowy adventures, the children are kept entertained. Once exhausted from the day's excitement, a cozy sleeping area with cots awaits, inviting them to drift off into sweet dreams."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "richtext",
            "text": [
                {
                    "type": "link",
                    "class": "font-bold uppercase tracking-wide",
                    "target": "_blank",
                    "url":"https://wengen.swiss/en/discover/routes-and-tours/articles/.html#area=60825264&cat=Hiking-main,Hiking%20Trail,25143811,Nature%20Trail,Biking%20and%20Cycling-main,Cycling,Mountain%20Bike,Road%20Bike,Running%20and%20Skating-main,Jogging,Trail%20Running,Mountaineering-main,Via%20Ferrata,Mountain%20Hike,Winter%20Activities-main,Winter%20Hiking,Sledding,Snowshoeing,Cross-Country%20Skiing,City%20Walking,Promenade%20Route&dmdtab=oax-tab1&filter=r-fullyTranslatedLangus-,r-onlyOpened-,sb-sortedBy-0&ipd=44216349&wt=Wengen%20(Switzerland)%0A60825264&zc=12,7.95743,46.57857",
                    "value": "Fox Run Wengen: "
                },
                {
                    "type":"text",
                    "value": "Experience exhilarating sledging adventures alongside and above the iconic Lauberhorn downhill course."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "class": "mt-10",
            "text": [
                "In conclusion, Wengen stands as a gateway to unparalleled hiking adventures within the majestic Jungfrau region. With a plethora of activities catering to every preference, from leisurely walks to challenging summits, Wengen beckons nature lovers to embark on unforgettable journeys amidst breathtaking landscapes. We invite you to share your Wengen hiking experiences in the comments below and spread the word by sharing this post with fellow explorers. Let's inspire each other to discover the wonders of Wengen together!"
            ]
        }
